divs: Sighting DetailsSaw an object over Colne, Lancashire, UK, on Google earth. Shaped like a 30 mile wide square hat. Shadow cast exact shape and size 6.6 miles away from object. I called mufon. Object moved towards Keighly, Bradford, then north about 10 miles. By the time I began this it had completely disappeared. Love, light and luck to you all.
